//Mail.json
    "HnH.OwlStatueSpawned": "Greetings. You have been chosen, young adept.^^ Enclosed are instructions for crafting idols in the likeness of the being that has revealed itself to you.   ^^   -M. Rasmodius, Wizard%item craftingRecipe 95 %%%item craftingRecipe 54 %%[letterbg 2][#]Owl Eyes On You",
    "HnH.CCWarpTotem": "Mornin', farmer!^^ I see you've shipped a few of those owl feathers. Thought I'd share this recipe might help with your fishin' journey.   ^^   -Willy%item craftingRecipe 856 %%[#]Lured in by Curiosity",
    "HnH.CuriosityLure": "Greetings, young adept.^^ Enclosed is a totem manuscript attuned to my tower. Should you find yourself in need of my counsel, invoke it and you will be brought directly to me.   ^^   -M. Rasmodius, Wizard%item craftingRecipe 7thAxis.HnH_ForestWarpTotem %%[letterbg 2][#]A Forest Shortcut",
    "HnH.LargeIncubator": "Hi there, @!^^ I heard you've got yourself a barn. Congratulations! I wanted to let you know we now have Large Incubators in stock, they work great for larger birds.   ^^   -Marnie[#]A Large Incubator Near You!",
    "HnH.EggSpawned": "Hi, @!^^ Demetrius told me some abandoned owl eggs have been showing up in the forest. I'm now offering a special building to house the poor little critters. Feel free to stop by and check it out!   ^^   -Robin[#]The Boggy Aviary",
    "HnH.LeahGift": "Hi @!^^ Is it true you have owls on your farm? You might like this old owl painting guide I had laying around collecting dust! It's okay, I've already used it to death. I also included one of my prints!  ^^   -Leah%item id (O)7thAxis.HnH_HowToPaintOwls 1%%%item id (F)7thAxis.HnH_LeahOwlPainting%%[#]A Hoot-tastic Book!",
    "HnH.SnailStiltOwlScareCrow": "Hello, my cave-in savior!^^ I've heard through the grape vine that you discovered the egg of an owl thought to be long extinct... In celebration, take this decorative Stilt Owl! The legs should be completely accurate to the real bird.  ^^   -Professor Snail%item id (BC)7thAxis.HnH_StiltOwlScareCrow 1%%[#]An Owl On Stilts",
